*install*

https://github.com/bumptech/montage
https://github.com/bumptech/riak-haskell-client
https://github.com/wmoss/StatsWeb
-- install the dependencies
-- recommend installing them in a sandbox in a contrib folder

cabal install
-- installs Network.Riak.MontageClient
-- recommend using a sandbox, hsenv is nice


*examples*

runhaskell examples/basic_proxy.hs
-- proxy server

runhaskell examples/test_basic_proxy.hs
-- client tests basic commands

runhaskell examples/test_reference.hs
-- client tests reference get requests
